snippet.textDisplay: As a laymen with the music, I could say that bunch of things, make this song power pack. The main attraction of this song was with Banvari Devi mam, as she gave the amazing performance at top pitch as the entire piece from her is on top pitch. Secondly, I never heard / minimally heard any lady going for Rap and Hard Kaur did very well with it. The added advantage with the song was music, as it cant say whether it is with sync with song or the Echo of instruments, but when I listen this song, feel exited.

MTV...please try to put some sense into your songs. Making a good music does not mean ignoring lyrics!!!!!

Phony singers like this kaur were shown her place in this song. So called high pitch singer tonked out of the park and turned into Soft kaur, by the power and soul of Ms.Devi. 

Hope we get to see more pure performances by Ms.Devi instead of mashing it up with mediocre singers!
